    {
      "text": "Needs Review\n58\n{circled:\"52\"}\n\none binary organism spanning the two realms. Valis the deity punched into this realm (from outside, invading from the upper realm), impregnated me, and she is the result: she over there linked to me, part of me, and me part of her. Valis is gone back, now. But she remains, issuing out of Valis and me together, or out of Valis via me. (\"The channel of divinity by which it entered this world\" -- said of Mary.) Because she advises and informs me she speaks to this wo",
      "matched_alias": "Mary",
